---
title: Roasted Pepper Cavatappi Milano with Philadelphia Cream Cheese, Fresh Mozz, Crispy Panko & Chives
description: No matter the weather, it’s impossible not to daydream about a bubbly, soul-warming pasta dish. Well, folks, that dream is now a reality. This delicious dish has curly cavatappi and tender strips of roasted bell pepper cloaked in a creamy tomato-herb sauce. It’s topped off with fresh mozzarella and panko breadcrumbs before being broiled to gooey, golden-brown perfection. Yep, this one-pan wonder is guaranteed to satisfy all carby cravings. (We’re all about making dreams come true.)
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-pepper-cavatappi-milano-cef7081c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/roasted-pepper-cavatappi-milano-614b4697162828546b75f1ab-e4c7d828.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/roasted-pepper-cavatappi-milano-614b4697162828546b75f1ab
course: main course
cuisine: Italian
time required: 35 minutes
